# Book Descriptions – Source of Truth

When updating book descriptions in `src/data/books.ts`, use the canonical source and **copy descriptions exactly** (do not rewrite or paraphrase).

## Primary Source

**Book Info.csv** – `docs/Book Info.csv` (in project) or `c:\Users\Gus\Downloads\Book Info.csv`  
(Exported from: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17P2OUf5m-d63pu3Q_Kk5Cq6dTgSlT_9JeE9Cz0cRJJo/edit?usp=sharing)

Columns: `Book`, `eBay Item ID`, `description`, `link`  
Copy the `description` column exactly for each book. Match by book name or eBay Item ID to the `id` in `books.ts`.

